<div style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 640px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 2rem; background-color: #f8f9fa; border-radius: 8px; color: #212529;">

  <h2 style="margin-top: 0;">Welcome,</h2>

  <p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6;">
    You've been invited to join <strong><%= @resource.organization.name %></strong> on the <strong>Access Control App</strong>.
  </p>

  <p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6;">
    To accept this invitation and set your password, click the button below:
  </p>

  <p style="margin: 30px 0; text-align: center;">
    <a href="<%= accept_invitation_url(@resource, invitation_token: @token) %>"
       style="display: inline-block; padding: 12px 24px; background-color: #007bff; color: #fff; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 6px; font-size: 16px;">
      Accept Invitation
    </a>
  </p>

  <p style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6; color: #6c757d;">
    If the button above doesn’t work, you can copy and paste the following link into your browser:
  </p>

  <p style="font-size: 14px; word-break: break-all; background-color: #e9ecef; padding: 10px; border-radius: 4px; color: #343a40;">
    <%= accept_invitation_url(@resource, invitation_token: @token) %>
  </p>

  <p style="font-size: 14px; color: #6c757d; margin-top: 2rem;">
    If you weren’t expecting this invitation, you can safely ignore this email.
  </p>

  <p style="margin-top: 3rem; font-size: 14px;">
    Thanks,<br>
    <strong>The Access Control App Team</strong>
  </p>

</div>
